## Escalation Management Workflow

- [ ] 1. Identify the issue and its impact
- [ ] 2. Determine if escalation is needed (can the team resolve it?)
- [ ] 3. Prepare the escalation: context, options, recommendation
- [ ] 4. Escalate to the right person with the right information
- [ ] 5. Manage the resolution and communicate outcomes
- [ ] 6. Capture lessons learned to prevent recurrence

## Key Inputs
- Issue: {{issue}}
- Impact: {{impact}} (timeline, budget, client relationship)
- Options Considered: {{options_considered}}
- Recommendation: {{recommendation}}
- Escalation Path: {{escalation_path}}
